comments.body:
@PaulHigin, did you read how "https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/issues/17467#issuecomment-1149228070" states that "http://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/files/8856878/PowerShell_transcript.1653307616.%2BSym2k0I.20220601134519.txt" is able to invoke an identical reaction by the interpreter for me? It is a log that was created by recording invocation of the original file.

If you do not believe that that file allows reproduction, please observe the content of [this](https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/files/8958781/DEPICTION.ZIP). You shall need to be able to extract the tar.xz archive that is within it.

(I believe that all that is necessary to reproduce the problem are some corrupted characters at the end of the file.)
